text: Grant Roden (born 29 February 1980) is an Australian cricketer. He played one List A match for New South Wales in 2005/06. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
